<br>
Well, start one! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Organizations like this don't just spring up, they take at least a few people dedicated to making it work.  You don't have to start with raiding.  KCoG had done alot of &quot;just for fun&quot; stuff too, although not recently.  There have been human chess matches (at the Butcherblock chess board), drunken newbie races, and other events of the sort.  KCoG also does &quot;mixer hunts&quot; or mini-raids in  zones that aren't traditionally &quot;raid&quot; zones.<br>
<br>
I doubt any of the folks here will be starting any similar organizations on other servers, simply because we all play on Karana (those of us who still play).  However, feel free to take the idea and develop it on your own swerver. <p>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br>
