<br>
Some people will tell you that running a successful raid with their guild was a challenge, they should try to run that same raid with 50 people from 60 guilds  and see how well they do.  Serving a dog's breakfast and making it seem like haute cusiene was our greatest achievement.  <br>
<br>
Not only did we have people emailing us about our efforts, but we had GM's and guides drop by our meetings just to see and witness our achievements.  Also people would create characters on the Karana server just to participate in our fun events.  Dogedme's Walk was well attended from a few other servers for example.  <br>
<br>
KGoC served as my inspiration to help form the Albion Warlord Council in DAoC on Palomides and was a great tool to help us turn the tide in RvR at that time.  <br>
<br>
Silver Daggers have been a good influence for these reasons in my opinion.  <p>Truth is Truth</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showMessageRange?topicID=104.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showPrevMessage?topicID=104.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showNextMessage?topicID=104.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=104.topic&index=24><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.emailToFriend?topicID=104.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.threadControl?topicID=104.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=104.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fcouncilofguildscouncildiscussions.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=104.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub140.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><t